                            <comment id="15102" author="max" created="Sat, 22 Oct 2005 19:12:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Obviously, the poposed fix should be&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if (firstResult &amp;gt;= 0) { &lt;/p&gt;

